{"tid":174974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【估國家】煞車不及？大貨車衝撞小學生　多人遭輾「血肉模糊」釀3死","createTime":"2017-03-27T07:46:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-16T22:21:15.000Z","uid":22675,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9627b2e4f94c6e35b9067d2c1b1ab1b86b9965b1","tid":174974,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T07:46:03.000Z","msg":"大陸廣西貴港桂平市木樂鎮昨（25日）發生一起嚴重車禍，一輛大貨車駛經廣仁村路段時，高速撞向一大群正在過馬路的小學生，造成3人死亡、2人受傷，現場畫面血腥恐怖。今監視器畫面曝光，可見駕駛曾試圖煞停車輛，地上煞車痕相當清晰，詳細事故原因警方還在調查中。<br />\n<br />\n根據監視器畫面顯示，兩名老師先是在在雙程路的斑馬線兩旁擺放4個交通三角錐，提示雙向車道的駕駛小心，沒想到正當小學生們橫過馬路之際，一輛大貨車突然疾駛過來，疑似煞車不及，直接衝撞並輾壓數名學生。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另據民眾拍攝畫面，車禍現場一片狼藉，有名女童全身染滿鮮血，雙腳被輾至血肉模糊；另一名被撞學生的身體更慘遭大貨車輾碎，只剩一雙殘肢，地上一條長長的血痕；而路旁還有至少有兩名傷勢嚴重、身體多處受傷的小學生倒臥地上。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://pic.ctitv.com/wpimg/2017/03/bkncn-20170324201844156-0324_05011_001_01p_meitu_1_meitu_1.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.ctitv.com%2Fwpimg%2F2017%2F03%2Fbkncn-20170324201844156-0324_05011_001_01p_meitu_1_meitu_1.jpg&d=s93SzOo3lOnuHTfFtNogbQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=a8fa1f21\" target=\"_blank\">http://pic.ctitv.com/wpimg/2017/03/bkncn-20170324201844156-0324_05011_001_01p_meitu_1_meitu_1.jpg</a>(慎入)<br />\n<br />\n民眾拍攝現場畫面，現場一片狼藉，血腥恐怖。（圖／取自東網）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://pic.ctitv.com/wpimg/2017/03/bkncn-20170325153510343-0325_05011_001_06p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.ctitv.com%2Fwpimg%2F2017%2F03%2Fbkncn-20170325153510343-0325_05011_001_06p.jpg&h=62e7e266&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大批民眾憤怒衝上駕駛座。（圖／取自東網）<br />\n<br />\n事發後，大批民眾憤怒的衝上大貨車駕駛座，欲將司機拉下車，最後多名員警抵達制止，並在現場拉起封鎖線。據當地警方最新通報，肇事駕駛目前已被刑拘，事故原因仍在調查。（更多新聞就在中天快點TV）<br />\n<br />\n※觀看道路監視器影片請【點我】；民眾拍攝畫面請【點我】&rarr;血腥慎入!!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://pic.ctitv.com/wpimg/2017/03/bkncn-20170324201844156-0324_05011_001_05p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.ctitv.com%2Fwpimg%2F2017%2F03%2Fbkncn-20170324201844156-0324_05011_001_05p.jpg&h=e647b7d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n防暴警察在現場拉起封鎖線，並在大貨車四周築起人牆。（圖／取自東網）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://gotv.ctitv.com.tw/2017/03/435252.htm?from=fb_ct_news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgotv.ctitv.com.tw%2F2017%2F03%2F435252.htm%3Ffrom%3Dfb_ct_news&d=s93SzOo3lOnuHTfFtNogbQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=dbdf1316\" target=\"_blank\">http://gotv.ctitv.com.tw/2017/03/435252.htm?from=fb_ct_news</a>"},{"pid":"b09d7216bdc9b68778693bf860a6ef1b8bfc5a86","tid":174974,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T07:50:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"829056f09c2da8f293802077f3e2e37aae2fca05","tid":174974,"uid":51796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T07:52:37.000Z","msg":"慎入圖完全唔覺恐怖"},{"pid":"8b952f88657df453cc0c6e06eb0949dca7f554e8","tid":174974,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T08:03:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d87e528edf6ef80e7da0ce80ca2aab3a3ebebd2","tid":174974,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T08:09:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>防暴警察</blockquote><br />\n第一次聽車禍出防暴警察唔係交通警，我諗只有强國特色既炒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44c89dcb89ec0a90cf9659b5b6956dd18109ce5e","tid":174974,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T08:16:06.000Z","msg":"打保齡都係死3隻 渣ga<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"434a1cae8d92dcab23262873564e435f7d6f3cbb","tid":174974,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T08:52:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b017dfeb51c76b210e2ba2181f5d88e62612318","tid":174974,"uid":48622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T08:55:1